      "Momentum": "Momentum factor (positive = trend-following wins)",
      "Volatility": "Volatility regime change (positive = VIX-like measure UP); negative loading means asset is hurt by vol spikes",
      "RealRate": "Real interest rate change (positive = real rates UP); negative loading means asset is hurt by rate hikes",
      "Inflation": "Inflation expectations change (positive = inflation UP); positive loading means inflation hedge",
      "CreditSpread": "Credit spread change (positive = spreads WIDEN); negative loading means asset is hurt by credit risk"
    },
    "method": "heuristic",
    "lookup_order": "per_symbol > loadings (by class)"
